a-icon="tabler:briefcase" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em"><symbol id="ai:tabler:briefcase"><g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M3 9a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v9a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2zm5-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h4a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v2m-4 5v.01"/><path d="M3 13a20 20 0 0 0 18 0"/></g></symbol><use xlink:href="#ai:tabler:briefcase"></use></svg><div class="font-bold text-xl">CRN</div><p class="text-center mt-2 text-secondary">Former technology entrepreneur with expertise in edge markets and emergent commercialization.</p></div><a class="block" href="https://pkd.unsuspicious.org"><div class="flex items-center flex-col backdrop-blur p-8 relative rounded-lg"><svg class="mb-2 flex-shrink-0 h-10 text-primary w-10" data-icon="tabler:brain" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em"><symbol id="ai:tabler:brain"><g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M15.5 13a3.5 3.5 0 0 0-3.5 3.5v1a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 7 0v-1.8M8.5 13a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 3.5 3.5v1a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-7 0v-1.8"/><path d="M17.5 16a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0-7H17"/><path d="M19 9.3V6.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0-7 0M6.5 16a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0-7H7"/><path d="M5 9.3V6.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 7 0v10"/></g></symbol><use xlink:href="#ai:tabler:brain"></use></svg><div class="font-bold text-xl">PKD</div><p class="text-center mt-2 text-secondary">Research director specializing in computational systems, artificial intelligence, and mathematical modeling.</p></div></a></div></div></section><section class="relative not-prose scroll-mt-[72px]"><div class="inset-0 pointer-events-none absolute -z-[1]" aria-hidden="true"><div class="inset-0 -z-10 fixed overflow-hidden"><astro-island await-children="" client="load" component-export="default" component-url="/assets/js/spacetime-fabric.js" opts="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SpacetimeFabric&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}" prefix="r1" props="{}" renderer-url="/assets/js/client.js" ssr="" uid="Z2l0PYD"><div class="inset-0 pointer-events-none -z-10 fixed" style="width:100vw;height:100vh"></div></astro-island></div></div><div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:py-12 md:px-6 md:py-10 py-8 text-default"><div class="mb-6 max-w-3xl md:mb-12 md:mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center"><h2 class="font-bold font-heading leading-tighter tracking-tighter md:text-4xl sm:text-3xl text-2xl text-heading">Research Faculty & Staff</h2></div><div class="gap-4 grid grid-fade md:gap-6 sm:gap-y-8"><div class="flex items-center flex-col backdrop-blur p-8 relative rounded-lg"><svg class="mb-2 flex-shrink-0 h-10 text-primary w-10" data-icon="tabler:school" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em"><symbol id="ai:tabler:school"><g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 9L12 5L2 9l10 4zv6"/><path d="M6 10.6V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-5.4"/></g></symbol><use xlink:href="#ai:tabler:school"></use></svg><div class="font-bold text-xl">Thomas C.</div><p class="text-center mt-2 text-secondary">Research Assistant in Computational Engineering. Engineering student.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="relative not-prose scroll-mt-[72px]"><div class="inset-0 pointer-events-none absolute -z-[1]" aria-hidden="true"><div class="inset-0 -z-10 fixed overflow-hidden"><astro-island await-children="" client="load" component-export="default" component-url="/assets/js/spacetime-fabric.js" opts="{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;SpacetimeFabric&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:true}" prefix="r2" props="{}" renderer-url="/assets/js/client.js" ssr="" uid="Z2l0PYD"><div class="inset-0 pointer-events-none -z-10 fixed" style="width:100vw;height:100vh"></div></astro-island></div></div><div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 lg:py-12 md:px-6 md:py-10 py-8 text-default"><div class="mb-6 max-w-3xl md:mb-12 md:mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center"><h2 class="font-bold font-heading leading-tighter tracking-tighter md:text-4xl sm:text-3xl text-2xl text-heading">Institutional Divisions</h2></div><div class="gap-4 grid grid-fade md:gap-6 sm:gap-y-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 px-4 sm:px-6"><div class="flex flex-col backdrop-blur relative rounded-lg bg-ft border border-[var(--aw-color-bg-fancy)] p-4 shadow-[0_4px_30px_var(--aw-color-bg-fancy)] sm:p-6"><svg class="mb-6 h-12 text-accent w-12" data-icon="tabler:building-bank" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em"><symbol id="ai:tabler:building-bank"><path d="M3 21h18M3 10h18M5 6l7-3l7 3M4 10v11m16-11v11M8 14v3m4-3v3m4-3v3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"/></symbol><use xlink:href="#ai:tabler:building-bank"></use></svg><div class="font-bold text-xl">Research Administration</div><p class="text-muted mt-2">Our Research Administration oversees money, people and make sure projects are coherent. The only barrier between us and LLM-psychosis.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col backdrop-blur relative rounded-lg bg-ft border border-[var(--aw-color-bg-fancy)] p-4 shadow-[0_4px_30px_var(--aw-color-bg-fancy)] sm:p-6"><svg class="mb-6 h-12 text-accent w-12" data-icon="tabler:school" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em"><use xlink:href="#ai:tabler:school"></use></svg><div class="font-bold text-xl">Defining Division</div><p class="text-muted mt-2">The Defining Division defines everything we say. Good discussions and research must start with clear definitions and outlines of concepts.</p></div><div class="flex flex-col backdrop-blur relative rounded-lg bg-ft border border-[var(--aw-color-bg-fancy)] p-4 shadow-[0_4px_30px_var(--aw-color-bg-fancy)] sm:p-6"><svg class="mb-6 h-12 text-accent w-12" data-icon="tabler:book-2" height="1em" viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="1em"><symbol id="ai:tabler:book-2"><g fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 4v16H7a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2z"/><path d="M19 16H7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2M9 8h6"/></g></symbol><use xlink:href="#ai:tabler:book-2"></use></svg><div class="font-bold text-xl">Publications &amp; Outreach</div><p class="text-muted mt-2">Our Publications division manages peer review processes, academic conferences, public engagement initiatives, and knowledge transfer programs that disseminate our research to broader communities.</p></div></div></div></section><div class="quote-block" data-astro-cid-xht55kip><div class="quote-ornament" data-astro-cid-xht55kip>‹‹</div><blockquote class="quote-text" data-astro-cid-xht55kip>The truth may be puzzling. It may take some work to grapple with. It may be counterintuitive. It may contradict deeply held prejudices. It may not be consonant with what we desperately want to be true. But our preferences do not determine what&#39;s true.</blockquote><div class="quote-attribution" data-astro-cid-xht55kip><span class="quote-author" data-astro-cid-xht55kip>Carl Sagan</span> <span class="quote-citation" data-astro-cid-xht55kip>Cosmos</span></div><div class="quote-ornament quote-ornament-end" data-astro-cid-xht55kip>››</div></div></main>
